ast maxed out the Razorback troop capactiy, there would be less hate. <p>&quot;... whereever you rub it, it always feels better, ...&quot; - Brak</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/bheavyhand65062.showUserPublicProfile?gid=phantomnomad@heavyhand65062>phantom nomad</A> at: 3/5/03 11:32:29 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=404040><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/bheavyhand65062.showUserPublicProfile?gid=drgabe>DrGabe</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://heavyhand.org/portent-avatar.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>King of the Message Board</span><br>  Posts: 859<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/6/03 2:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://heavyhand.org/avatar18.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Take a gander at this one...</span><hr size=1> His min-maxing doesn't help his argument much.<br>
